Product_name: Lenovo Smart Tab M10 with Google Assistant and Google Kids Space
Product_description: The Lenovo Smart Tab M10 HD is a stunning media tablet. On its own, the 10.1" device comes in a sleek profile, with an all-aluminum design, fast connectivity, powerful processing and a media center with Dolby Atmos® optimized dual speakers. When the device is idle, dock it onto the smart charging station to charge and transform it into your hands-free smart home hub. With Google Assistant’s Ambient Mode, you can get more done hands-free. Manage your daily schedule, get your answers quickly, request your favourite playlist or news, and control your smart home devices - all with just your voice. From front to back, top to bottom, the full metal body cover provides a modern touch. The narrow bezels on the display help to provide a jaw-dropping 87% screen-to-display ratio. With dual speakers expertly tuned with Dolby Atmos®, everything sounds better. From games to movies and music, the truly immersive sounds you hear and feel will transport you to the center of the action. Enjoy the new Kids Mode for the younger ones. Google Kids Space is designed for kids ages 3 to 8 and works with your child’s Google Account, that parents can help manage with Family Link. It is designed to nurture your kid’s curiosity and creativity, inspiring them to explore their interests through thoughtfully curated apps, books, and videos. Set your device onto the Smart Charging Station for hassle-free charging. With the Google Assistant’s Ambient Mode, you can transform your tablet into a media center: use it as a digital photo frame, listen to music, watch videos, manage smart home devices, and get key updates, such as the morning traffic, news, and weather.

LINSAY F7XHDBKZEBRA with WiFi 7" Touchscreen Tablet PC:   Technical Specifications:  1.20GHz Quad-Core processor Android 9.0 Pie 2 GB DDR3 of system memory 16 GB storage 7" touchscreen, 1024 x 600 HD Screen resolution, and virtual keyboard Built-in 802.11b/g/n WiFi  Additional Features:  Dual HD Webcams with microphone 1 x headphone jack, 1 x USB 2.0 port 16GB onboard storage memory, additional memory via microSD card slot Built-in stereo speaker G-sensor Weighs 2.0 lbs; 7.5" x 1.5" x 3.8" dimensions  Software and Applications:  Android 9.0 Pie  What's in the Box:  Tablet AC adapter Keyboard case   What's a Tablet PC?  Tablet PCs are compact, ultra-portable entertainment devices that let you read email, surf the Internet, read eBooks, view photos, play games, listen to music and watch video files. Most tablets are based on a smaller operating system, which allows you to purchase and download additional applications from supported stores. Tablet PCs do not have a CD/DVD drive and will not run Microsoft Windows or its applications. Tablet PCs function as a secondary device for casual entertainment purposes and are not meant to replace a computer. They are ideal for use around the home and on the go with WiFi or 3-4G mobile broadband connections (pay as you go, contract may be required for service).
